author: Lorraine%20Weibgen
title: Lorraine%20Weibgen
text: My review is positive as I found an easy going tenant who is perfect to meet the criteria I required. This all happened in a week. I responded to four people but none of them replied to me except Luke and is such a find. Would be an advantage if there was someway to know if someone received your reply but otherwise a great experience m. Thank you. Lorraine
